title: American Horror Stories Episode 5 Review "Ba Al"
author: Reel Talk
comment: Strongest episode of American Horror Stories yet!  <3 Billie Lourd

I feel like Billie Lourd was good. Her lack of affect makes sense after the mental and physical drain of years of fertility treatment . Once the baby was born, she was sleep deprived and thought she was going crazy.
This episode in my opinion is the best one so far, Billie Lourd’s acting was on point. Last week’s episode was in my opinion absolute trash I’m sorry. No more bro house 😅

Remember all: When dealing with a totem you can't just throw it away and must dispose of it responsibly. A closure spell may be needed. Take totem to a professional like Cordelia or a voodoo queen. Fiona may also help with this.
Even though these episodes aren’t that great I still I like them but I feel like what Ryan should’ve did was do random stories around America ( if that make sense ) with different serial killers
